{"tid":2047670,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Twitter戰線,成日老奉要外國關注同幫香港","createTime":"2020-06-02T09:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T21:53:25.000Z","uid":175309,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"167d3b8cfb9278a9ce2e3bd3e830fbab0d2e7058","tid":2047670,"uid":175309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qcM3brF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqcM3brF.jpg&h=6a163f0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有一班twitter線既人<br />\n長期用一種居高臨下又挑釁既語氣去叫人關注香港<br />\n上圖呢條友係反中既內地人<br />\n名就唔撚幫佢遮了,可以自己去search下佢既留言<br />\n<br />\n而家不乏一堆香港人留言屌外國人<br />\n屌外國人跪死黑人就咁大反應<br />\n香港搞到咁就wfc<br />\n<br />\n屌同班小粉紅有乜撚分別?<br />\n搞到神憎鬼厭<br />\n<br />\n求其他手足幫手,見呢種中就留言屌佢地<br />\n唔好俾佢地代表左香港人"},{"pid":"594a52be2beedf89c63ddc82e9a89b1abec97924","tid":2047670,"uid":175309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:08:14.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"7541ff9077b593a512ac5161a59f9f5ca48946bb","tid":2047670,"uid":134840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37cc2c78b28ab06fd7ddae1d6248169e83f45bbd","tid":2047670,"uid":175309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2cb6afb3886270fd6d3f210d801adecb6950c1","tid":2047670,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:12:24.000Z","msg":"唔好介入去安全<br />\n如果有人係要介入 要睇吓佢係咪中共狗"},{"pid":"a4362585f9393c193ad1237870377536d8938df8","tid":2047670,"uid":175309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf2cb6afb3886270fd6d3f210d801adecb6950c1","tid":2047670,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi